  "title": "10 round blue UFOs were spotted in Brasília-DF",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/01/10-round-blue-ufos-were-spotted-in-brasilia-df/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1jQ",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>NOV 20th, 1994</strong>. Time: 23:20. Duration: 5 minutes. From the Asa Norte region in Brasília, Distrito Federal, one person spotted ten small unidentified flying objects, with circular shapes and light blue color. According to the witness, the UFOs were flying close to each other at an altitude of about 500 meters. The sighting was carried out in cloudy sky with the naked eye. There were no reports of photographs or filming of the event.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.382. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Brasília, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>NOV 20th, 1994. Time: 23:20. Duration: 5 minutes. From the Asa Norte region in Brasília, Distrito Federal, one person spotted ten small unidentified flying objects, with circular shapes and light blue color. According to the witness, the UFOs were flying close to each other at an altitude of about 500 meters. The sighting was carried [&hellip;]</p>\n",
